{"tid":2488352,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"其實搭巴士返工既人係咪普遍比較冇文化","createTime":"2021-04-14T07:28:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T08:42:32.000Z","uid":1930,"like":3,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"360ce6f103c45ec09adae2aeaa9081f9c935d535","tid":2488352,"uid":1930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T07:28:54.000Z","msg":"話說小弟之前都係搭開港鐵返工，但因為好多時要企同埋要轉勁多次車，所以呢排開始試搭巴士返工（冷知識：我諗大家都唔知，原來荃灣去沙田搭巴士仲快過港鐵，呢樣真係估佢唔到！）<br />\n<br />\n雖然又快左又有位坐，但我發現搭巴士既人唔知係咪比較窮，好多時候都好燥底同冇文化。譬如今朝我坐坐下個陣，發現前面條友成日向後望，我初頭都好有禮貌咁冇屌柒佢架啦，點知佢仲無端端惡人先告狀，話咩我隻腳頂住佢椅背，我心諗真係搞笑，咁小事都好嘈一餐，依家個坐位係我個範圍入面，大家都係比咁多錢搭車，點解我要讓你，不過我廢事同佢嘈，只係好精警咁串返佢一句「咁巴閉去搭的士」囉，跟住佢比我串到冇聲出，仲企左起身，我初頭以為佢想打鳩我，但原來佢係度望我後面有冇位，我估佢應該係想坐我後面頂返我？但咁岩我個位後面有人坐，所以佢即刻收左皮走左落樓下。<br />\n<br />\n但唔知係我唔好彩遇到呢d燥底西人定真係普遍搭巴士既人都比較低質，所以想上黎問下搭開巴士既巴絲點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\np.s. 今朝條燥底西人如果你睇到post就去睇下醫生啦，少少野就發爛渣應該係有燥狂症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a480cbe2da6bd4823cd44db68adebff1629f4aa7","tid":2488352,"uid":137038,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T07:31:44.000Z","msg":"你諗下城隧線係來往咩地方返工就知低質係正常<br />\n港島路線會好啲"},{"pid":"b6a2ba9a6c810f61bb1f905f26629c943623996a","tid":2488352,"uid":1399,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T07:32:34.000Z","msg":"我坐開的士"},{"pid":"eb372a9e49c40b0d6e32dd242ee2b7a19960283c","tid":2488352,"uid":137725,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T07:35:01.000Z","msg":"搭得巴士或者地鐵呀 都唔會有文化得去邊啦<br />\n使乜分咁細<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6d58140b282afaeaafa4e55fa5bb2200b34de3f","tid":2488352,"uid":397108,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T07:35:02.000Z","msg":"唔返工最有文化<br />\n你呢d要搭車返工既多數都係傻閪黎"},{"pid":"59c06220ed8d15051f240acc05ca1556a259b5a5","tid":2488352,"uid":394002,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T07:35:49.000Z","msg":"但你隻腳頂住佢椅背<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"134dfc8d6fe54fb2556f5ca047f71739eb687272","tid":2488352,"uid":1777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T07:36:09.000Z","msg":"yes"},{"pid":"80aadfeaa3376ab30ddb555d303462d383c37c71","tid":2488352,"uid":223084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T07:36:41.000Z","msg":"地鐵仲痴線過巴士"},{"pid":"b56d1963ad7b6d3617941481161aefc7dc42a813","tid":2488352,"uid":312430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T07:38:22.000Z","msg":"你試下咁講<br />\n你有壓力，我有壓力，你做乜挑釁我呀？"},{"pid":"330503c9023b2337a14c529add7f3ecd03bf6d78","tid":2488352,"uid":213295,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T07:39:03.000Z","msg":"你頂人背脊有文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"a7f684c27101ae1485f9620fd1d682685926ffa9","tid":2488352,"uid":45144,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T07:40:20.000Z","msg":"你頂鳩人,  係我都屌你啦"},{"pid":"d895c03ca2ab23485f635a67d7dc70f845f26c36","tid":2488352,"uid":33635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T07:41:10.000Z","msg":"垃圾假膠POST<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca363ad1a82fb9ba0035782a97db0f64d6c53ea2","tid":2488352,"uid":154671,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T07:41:34.000Z","msg":"坐巴士最憎後面隻腳頂住個椅背，勁無文化，試下比人頂住個個係佢睇佢坐得舒唔舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29e3801106a4197dfbdbdded98eec0ba8ee78256","tid":2488352,"uid":199518,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T07:42:22.000Z","msg":"（冷知識：我諗大家都唔知，原來荃灣去沙田搭巴士仲快過港鐵，呢樣真係估佢唔到！）<br />\n睇到呢度已經知唔洗睇落去"},{"pid":"00c621f79ff138a25d0cb1d4dadec76c4f478559","tid":2488352,"uid":115910,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T07:43:44.000Z","msg":"我公司啲清潔呀姐搭私人直昇機返工但份人就認真麻麻<br />\n所以應該同交通工具無關係"},{"pid":"90dcc36577227655fd338e134bc80b2bd09ce703","tid":2488352,"uid":153976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T07:43:55.000Z","msg":"要返工仲有咩文化可言<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f23d2664fa84da323798f9fa4cf74edc17fcf93e","tid":2488352,"uid":20295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29e3801106a4197dfbdbdded98eec0ba8ee78256","tid":2488352,"uid":199518,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T07:42:22.000Z","msg":"（冷知識：我諗大家都唔知，原來荃灣去沙田搭巴士仲快過港鐵，呢樣真係估佢唔到！）<br />\n睇到呢度已經知唔洗睇落去"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T07:46:19.000Z","msg":"睇到呢句直接碌落去睇下大家講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1fd8670580e24a24c9f2213cd14325f3405f402","tid":2488352,"uid":258894,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T07:47:17.000Z","msg":"咁多野講咪搭番你嘅黨鐵囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你老母臭西<br />\n坐公共交通工具就係要有禮儀<br />\n盡量係唔影響其他人嘅情況下一齊搭<br />\n你話你原來1米8幾隻腳一定會頂住咁我冇野講<br />\n咪好聲同番人哋講隻腳真係冇位<br />\n唔係嘅你根本有位單純坐得衰就食屎啦<br />\n影響其他人重要串柒柒<br />\n下次唔差在帶埋hifi上車播歌啦<br />\n重以為自己比咗錢上車就大晒<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0277741ab41c205ffda33e087bf88d735337525","tid":2488352,"uid":262301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T08:11:26.000Z","msg":"你用腳頂住人背脊然後話人無文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab08636a9da6a27f03ada86b8b78c02abf3c5e03","tid":2488352,"uid":383914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T08:16:23.000Z","msg":"如果用黑絲腳頂人個椅背<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪會突然變得好有文化？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c91d7a3216fc2eb1953a9e3cff56119234f8fb9","tid":2488352,"uid":347978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab08636a9da6a27f03ada86b8b78c02abf3c5e03","tid":2488352,"uid":383914,"like":0,"dislike":0,